<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>SoulUnison - A World of Living Tales</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-black text-white font-sans">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-6">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-4">Welcome to SoulUnison</h1>
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl max-w-2xl">A fairytale world not for children, but for dreamers, rebels, and soul-seekers.</p>
    <a href="#about" class="mt-8 inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-white text-black font-semibold rounded-full hover:bg-gray-200 transition">Discover the World</a>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="py-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-black to-gray-900 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">What is SoulUnison?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      SoulUnison is not a storybook. It's a world waiting to be co-created. Here, your imagination builds cities, your fears shape forests, and your hopes bring characters to life. Nothing is preset â€” everything begins from the soul.
    </p>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
